    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>眼望天空</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在矿井深处开始你的旅程，你的数据库中没有记忆，你的程序中也没有指令。你唯一能看到的就是远处坍塌的矿井下的一丝亮光。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>每一次跳跃和手持都会让你离目标更近。探索不同的生物群落，面对不同的挑战，一路向上。</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>每个生物群落都会带来新的挑战</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144110/extras/9604955596f8582471d8e266d721d058.poster.avif?t=1758806400\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144110/extras/9604955596f8582471d8e266d721d058.webm?t=1758806400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144110/extras/9604955596f8582471d8e266d721d058.mp4?t=1758806400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>单人或多人模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144110/extras/9e6514d8085ca40eb2780b9817d1080d.poster.avif?t=1758806400\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144110/extras/9e6514d8085ca40eb2780b9817d1080d.webm?t=1758806400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144110/extras/9e6514d8085ca40eb2780b9817d1080d.mp4?t=1758806400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>逼真的攀爬物理效果</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144110/extras/d4ce3e3a53f4b83bba890527f8fbddc9.poster.avif?t=1758806400\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://sh